[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":323},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20210102\u002F1186303391\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20210102\u002F1186303391\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20210102\u002F1186303391\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20210102\u002F1186303391\u002F":298,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20210102\u002F1186303391\u002F":307},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2021\u002F01\u002F02\u002Fcustomize-github-profile-with-readme-stats\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":283,"date":284,"description":18,"extension":86,"lang":285,"meta":286,"navigation":103,"path":287,"readingMinutes":288,"seo":289,"standalone":290,"stem":291,"tags":292,"tldr":295,"updated":295,"url":296,"__hash__":297},"content\u002F雜談\u002F美化自己的-GitHub-首頁.md","美化自己的 GitHub 首頁","1186303391",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":275},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,33,36,47,50,54,61,71,82,126,129,134,138,151,177,180,185,204,211,214,253,259,262,271],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"最近看到一些人美化自己 GitHub 的首頁，所以就想紀錄一下該如何美化自己的首頁。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"建立-github","建立 GitHub",[16,24,25],{},"首先必須先建立一個與自己使用者名稱相同的儲存庫(Repositories)",[16,27,28],{},[29,30],"img",{"alt":31,"src":32},"Repositories","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-01-02%2023.46.47.png",[16,34,35],{},"基本上當你建立與自己名稱相同的儲存庫時，底下就會出現這個訊息了",[37,38,44],"pre",{"className":39,"code":41,"language":42,"meta":43},[40],"language-text","You found a secret! hsiangfeng\u002Fhsiangfeng is a ✨special ✨ repository that you can use to add a README.md to your GitHub profile. Make sure it’s public and initialize it with a README to get started. \n","text","",[45,46,41],"code",{"__ignoreMap":43},[16,48,49],{},"簡單來講，這個方式是一個特殊的儲存庫(我統稱「個人描述儲存庫)」，你可以用這個儲存庫來作為自己的描述，如果你懶的建立個人網頁介紹自己的話，其實這也是一個不錯的選擇。",[12,51,53],{"id":52},"建立-readmemd","建立 README.md",[16,55,56,57,60],{},"接下來就直接將專案給 ",[45,58,59],{},"git clone"," 下來吧。",[16,62,63,64],{},"然後再建立一個 README.md，基本上就是以 MD 格式撰寫為主，你只要撰寫完畢並上傳儲存庫，你的 GitHub 首頁就會出現這些描述了，但是這邊我想額外美化一下，也就是我希望首頁可以呈現我儲存庫的技術列表，因此我發現到這個專案 ",[65,66,70],"a",{"href":67,"rel":68},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fanuraghazra\u002Fgithub-readme-stats",[69],"nofollow","github-readme-stats",[16,72,73,74,77,78,81],{},"github-readme-stats 主要是用於優化這個「個人描述儲存庫」，基本上它是採用動態生成的，使用的方法非常簡單，依照官方名稱只需要將以下 ",[45,75,76],{},"?username="," 更改成自己的使用者名稱就可以了，例如我的是 ",[45,79,80],{},"hsiangfeng"," 那麼就只需要在自己的 README.md 寫入以下即可",[37,83,87],{"className":84,"code":85,"language":86,"meta":43,"style":43},"language-md shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","# README\n\n![Anurag's github stats](https:\u002F\u002Fgithub-readme-stats.vercel.app\u002Fapi?username=hsiangfeng)\n\n","md",[45,88,89,98,105],{"__ignoreMap":43},[90,91,94],"span",{"class":92,"line":93},"line",1,[90,95,97],{"class":96},"s-VM4","# README\n",[90,99,101],{"class":92,"line":100},2,[90,102,104],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":103},true,"\n",[90,106,108,112,116,119,123],{"class":92,"line":107},3,[90,109,111],{"class":110},"sMAXC","![",[90,113,115],{"class":114},"sTRMh","Anurag's github stats",[90,117,118],{"class":110},"](",[90,120,122],{"class":121},"sajvY","https:\u002F\u002Fgithub-readme-stats.vercel.app\u002Fapi?username=hsiangfeng",[90,124,125],{"class":110},")\n",[16,127,128],{},"最後只需要上傳該 README.md 你的首頁就會出現囉",[16,130,131],{},[29,132],{"alt":80,"src":133},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202021-01-02%2023.58.39.png",[12,135,137],{"id":136},"調整-github-readme-stats","調整 github-readme-stats",[16,139,140,141,146,147,150],{},"github-readme-stats 其實有非常多的樣式，你可以在這個 ",[65,142,145],{"href":143,"rel":144},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fanuraghazra\u002Fgithub-readme-stats\u002Fblob\u002Fmaster\u002Fthemes\u002FREADME.md",[69],"儲存庫"," 找到而修改的方式只是多一個參數即可 ",[45,148,149],{},"?theme=THEME_NAME","，舉例來我滿喜歡 Vue 的配色，所以我的參數就改成以下即可",[37,152,154],{"className":84,"code":153,"language":86,"meta":43,"style":43},"# README\n\n![Anurag's github stats](https: